Introduction

KARD is a four-member co-ed group under DSP Media. They officially debuted on July 19, 2017, with the mini album Hola Hola.

Prior to their debut, the group released three pre-debut singles: "Oh NaNa" on December 13, 2016, followed by "Don't Recall" on February 16, 2017, and "Rumor" on April 24, 2017.

Their name stands for King, Ace, JokeR, & HiDden.
